headline: Disney Signs DraftKings as ESPN’s New Sports-Betting Partner
summary: Starting on Dec. 1, players will be able to access the DraftKings’ sportsbook, daily fantasy contests and other products through the ESPN sites, according to a statement Thursday from the two companies.
